{"tid":259763,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"今日終於見識到動物台毒撚既威力","createTime":"2017-05-27T08:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T08:27:21.000Z","uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"410251ae0ea96ecb713fe240ec4dc7b2f77c9826","tid":259763,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:04:00.000Z","msg":"話說細佬我今日屁忽痕無野做,見到有位巴打開左台播動漫歌<br />\n咁細佬我都唔係唔睇動漫既人(輕音少女、明星學生妹之類既都睇過)<br />\n咁就好奇入去聽下啦,開頭D歌都好地地,突然殺出一首細佬我覺得好難聽既唔知咩歌黎<br />\n咁我咪打句好難聽,點知依句野刺激到班毒撚圍插我<br />\n話我ON9,叫我去死.....痴線,我會唔會成為香港回歸以來第一個因為話首歌難聽而死既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下係我同某最痴線果位毒撚既部分對話<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我都係話首歌難聽姐,首歌又唔係你唱既..<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :首歌係我點既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我撚知係你點架咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我撚知你唔鐘意聽<br />\n(大佬,依家無話你一定要知我鐘唔鐘意聽,亦無話唔俾你點,我由頭到尾都只係話首歌難聽姐)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :依家你一句引起人地圍,係邊個錯?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :一句難聽有咁大迴響?我有咩錯?而且好似都唔關你事..<br />\n跟住佢就舉左個例子將我話首歌難聽依個行為比喻為打人,咁佢就係申張正義既路人,仲話係我錯<br />\n我屌佢老尾我生平見過咁多人屈人都未屈到咁撚柒,用依D咁低級既誤導手法仲以為自己好威...<br />\n咁我就反駁..<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :如果你咁講,我都係針對首歌姐,又唔係針對點果個人,姐係我打緊舊石,你以為我打緊人,仲要過黎幫口,之後仲強詞奪理<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :舊石係我既!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...首歌係你既?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :係..有問題?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依個時候我終於明喇,原來我同緊個痴撚線既毒撚嘈,我恍然大悟,同依種癲佬嘈係無撚得贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我即刻打左句粗口屌柒佢然後ALT+F4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91dc118006e21830e69760a80ed4971b7cd19bfd","tid":259763,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:05:22.000Z","msg":"諗左幾耐"},{"pid":"1071295ffa2b2d12c632264c11db42776346cb1f","tid":259763,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:07:49.000Z","msg":"又....."},{"pid":"4e736a60110a3a53aaf176c1fe109e9a90273cf8","tid":259763,"uid":73119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"其實樓豬係咪暗串緊啲人話○○○係自己老婆，一有人鬧個角色就發癲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea900550b3a3a347f19da2253dc087b00522a93f","tid":259763,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又..........."},{"pid":"5a4006a7e01d0fbfc2a1fe2c8ad06a5b6b91ad80","tid":259763,"uid":5914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"閲"},{"pid":"3a8bfb3d512028dbe9df3017189eeb664baabc7d","tid":259763,"uid":47790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:12:06.000Z","msg":"動物台幾時改名做釣魚台?"},{"pid":"4c66ae9ac77e2eb1e5770757f8f206c4fea7998d","tid":259763,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n高質李依<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a4ffa02dd0295dc037b46b1c02b5c64d14c294","tid":259763,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n高質李依<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高質李依究竟有幾高質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18f2143cd6eca07bc999022908d0080cd552338","tid":259763,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"見到明星學生妹就知係釣魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c419308a122b33fece1266b41dbcd8723e52a0c","tid":259763,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"篇文有無十年？"}]}